"Fish, when found on an Ocean tile, gives 2 more food. For more information, "
"review the help for the individual tile type."
msgstr ""

#: data/civ1/terrain.ruleset:1254 data/civ2/terrain.ruleset:1454
#: data/civ2civ3/terrain.ruleset:1958 data/classic/terrain.ruleset:1755
#: data/experimental/terrain.ruleset:1775 data/multiplayer/terrain.ruleset:1727
#: data/royale/terrain.ruleset:1923 data/sandbox/game.ruleset:2043
