"- \"Allows units to be airlifted from allied cities\" (FROM_ALLIES).\n"
"- \"Allows units to be airlifted to allied cities\" (TO_ALLIES).\n"
"- \"Unlimited units from source city\" (SRC_UNLIMITED): note that airlifting "
